Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.53,0:00:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有多久才能登陆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会耽误和土影使者的汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也尽快赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受够了 感觉地面摇晃不止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来直到最后 凯的晕船症也没能好转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里补给完物资后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往雷之国的路就不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有些小意外 但还是顺利完成任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味噌豚骨虽然不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但海鲜的也不差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚停稳就飞奔了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正也要在这留宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且还是座小岛 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在晃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之国离这座小岛不远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是座小岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走得太远会给与我们接头的人添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啦 我们来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就抽空随便看看咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复得真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 土影大人委派我做使者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自跟来干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么见外嘛 赤土
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水之国一直未和我们建交
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没机会弄到情报呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过虽然联手了 但大家都是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见机行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是土影的使者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的小命…我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…我们是同盟国的忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦 去死吧 岩隐村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.38,0:02:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤土
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩隐和雾隐怎么在这里打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就打了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 木叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢阻挠的话 就算是木叶的也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别阻止我 长十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 这么做有违水影大人的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉命阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能做到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点…可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么要袭击我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是争执的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把他抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.77,0:04:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木叶打杂的 你也来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…打杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然没医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 这座岛屿非常偏僻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大部队里有医疗忍者 他们正赶往这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾我拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别汇报了 快擦汗去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个迟钝的杂役啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说谁是打杂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在这里转悠的 不就是些负责传令的杂役吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话 快干活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为啥要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 怎么会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才收到了水影大人的传令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里有数名忍者突然间失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是反对这次忍者同盟的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心人物就是上忍岩流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤了赤土的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他是绿之峡悲剧事件的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿之峡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您应该知道 雾隐同岩隐长期交恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.31,0:07:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起事件就是其中一条导火线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十多年前 曾收集各地忍术的云隐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢过我们村里的机密文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我们和同盟岩隐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由岩流带队 前去夺回文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心 云隐的那帮家伙就在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 附近有岩隐的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个任务如果能成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以向诸国证明 岩隐和雾隐的同盟坚若磐石
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 离和平又更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在期盼这一天的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是盟友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务就是将文件带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能饶恕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲 俊菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离和平又更近一步了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直憎恨着岩隐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的结盟或许是他无法容忍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到袭击我们的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许他想通过暗杀岩隐的使者来复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时破坏这个未曾抱有希望的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能被这些杂事干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被干掉之前先发制人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等…这件事是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我看好赤土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者的世界正被仇恨所支配
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我找不到答案的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就将答案托付给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是唱哪出啊 打杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解 因为同伴被伤 你很愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是别去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我坐以待毙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果去了 双方一定会有伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死的是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们互相残杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说些莫名其妙的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能阻止就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说不让你去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会放你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是个打杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会这么麻烦的拦路之术
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去交涉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你快回你同伴那儿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小瞧我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个使者离开了长十郎 正赶往这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎击吧 岩流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我一个人就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先回村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我的父亲被岩隐所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干一起干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替村活着的人多想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的愤怒和痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.82,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切恩怨都由我来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是木叶的漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾人柱力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道大叔的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我是来阻止大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的师父被佩因所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:14:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能理解大叔的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还请罢手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你已经干掉了佩因 报仇雪恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那家伙只是气数已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你没想过报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.65,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.12,0:14:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对他的时候 我无法抑制恨意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.64,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身颤抖 恨不得立刻杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道 这样是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为憎恨的轮回就此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦开始 复仇便会唤起复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的人们则不断死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些我早已心中有数
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:15:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想实现她的愿望只有一条路…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果此时引发复仇惨剧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五影们就会认真思考缔结这个同盟的困难和危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 为了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各村不过是为各自的利益而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子间的同盟也会因各自的利益而轻松瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 忍者们为了村子的利益不断背叛 对立 杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五大国之中 这个忍者世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道有多少人在敌视别国忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是我 下次就会是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会像你一样停止复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此肤浅的同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会不断重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会改变这样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何敢断言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我继承了师父和师兄的嘱托
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何消除仇恨的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何阻止复仇轮回的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何让忍者之间相互理解的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.48,0:16:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们二个信任我 我就一定要找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请大叔相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕进展缓慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会尽可能靠近和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.97,0:17:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离和平又更近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.43,0:17:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡莲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 岩流
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这紧要关头掺和进来干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 我可是全力砍下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不会死在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多事要做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…死了可就是我的责任了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国际纠纷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少开玩笑了 别死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…好痛啊 只是休息了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩涡鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不束手就擒的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.17,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会反抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 麻烦治好那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾忍的家伙 赤土呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医疗忍者到了我才过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说没有性命之忧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩流先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是受被你所伤的使者所托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将绿之峡牺牲的忍者的遗物归还
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及就那次事件正式谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是土影大人派遣使者前来的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩隐…竟然会为那起事件谢罪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个顽固的老头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了巩固我们和雾隐的同盟关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大叔 会怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是死罪就是流放吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟作出了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也该有所觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为不小心摔倒才受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 黑土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是为那起事件赎罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送雾隐一个人情嘛 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 不仅仅是老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会连你也被风影感化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾影的家伙 这只是给你们的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有木叶打杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有伤在身…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我的同伴还在等我 再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少报上姓名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这副惨状是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢 不小心摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了…在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青叶 吐槽点不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 明天还要早起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好出发准备 早点休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 关于这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来消息说雷之国的船只会直接来接我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙一定就是引导我的章鱼的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这家伙到底合不合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要说勉强也算合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:23:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大爷我自古讨厌小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个爱说冷笑话的肌肉大叔是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.49,0:23:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.35,0:23:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登陆 乐园之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大叔 是八尾人柱力
